.TH MSNAP 1HIPS "Febuary 17, 1988"
.SH NAME
msnap - capture a frame of video input through the matrox vip-1024 
frame grabber board(s).
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B msnap
[-c]
.SH DESCRIPTION 
.I Msnap 
captures a frame of video input through the matrox vip-1024 
GREEN COLORPLANE BOARD.
The 
.I -c 
option indicates that the video source is a color
camera (i.e., all three colorplanes are used).
.SH SEE\ ALSO
rframe(1HIPS), wframe(1HIPS), mclear(1HIPS), and mlive(1HIPS)
.SH AUTHOR
Edmond Mesrobian - 2/17/88
